	<article class="post-632132 post type-post status-publish hentry category-financial-services category-investment-banking category-legal category-the-trade tag-dodd-frank-wall-street-reform-and-consumer-protection-act-2010 tag-financial-stability-oversight-council tag-garrett-e-scott tag-regulation-and-deregulation-of-industry per-garrett-e-scott des-dodd-frank-wall-street-reform-and-consumer-protection-act-2010 des-regulation-and-deregulation-of-industry org-financial-stability-oversight-council news_keywords-dodd-frank-2 news_keywords-e-scott-garrett news_keywords-financial-stability-oversight-council news_keywords-regulation-and-deregulation" id="post-632132">
